description:
Service Usage

This service is designed to be able to retrieve a Person or Organisation based on the exact matching of names and biographic details. This differs from other services that utilise fuzzy name, linguistic and phonetic name matching techniques and instead focus's on the function where a surname or given name is known outright to discover other parties with that exact details and not cloud the results with additional logic.

Service Usage

This service is designed to be able to retrieve a Person or Organisation based on the exact matching of names and biographic details.
